{"tid":2344370,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「連登已死」屌奶星，拉科魯尼亞踢緊西丙無人講？","createTime":"2020-12-28T16:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T00:58:28.000Z","uid":16697,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"05e53d5c1c6b468a3bd8c1258da63f71e8faac88","tid":2344370,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T16:12:22.000Z","msg":"今季西班牙丙組球隊內，有一隊好熟悉嘅名字............拉科魯尼亞<br />\n<br />\n拉科魯尼亞球隊已經有118年歷史，有一段長時間係西甲嘅豪門名牌球隊之一，並喺1999-2000年度球季勇奪西甲最高榮譽........西甲冠軍，及曾4度奪西甲亞軍、4度奪西甲亞季軍，並曾擊敗AC米蘭打入歐聯決賽<br />\n<br />\n但近10年，拉科已由西甲前列球隊，退至西甲下游球隊，再退至西甲西乙升降機，今季更歷史性降落西丙<br />\n<br />\n仲要今季至今，喺西丙嘅成績都只係普通<br />\n<br />\n拉科，令人唏噓嘅球隊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬基爾，卓斯坦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240f5ad94ce840097256b0f69e8e3a834e47cb1e","tid":2344370,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T16:13:38.000Z","msg":"Wow old news is so exciting"},{"pid":"c2ba72d8bfa208ab1443233f58701efba1ae9684","tid":2344370,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T16:16:04.000Z","msg":"認真回下<br />\n佢地好似無入過歐聯決賽"},{"pid":"f4a7168cf65b24cb127b6336f625b2178a745c7d","tid":2344370,"uid":16697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T16:16:42.000Z","msg":"歐聯4作客1:4輸比A米，主場4:0反勝<br />\n<br />\n華拿朗<br />\n域陀<br />\n<br />\n皇馬連續廿年作客贏唔到拉科"},{"pid":"26401951a6b6c8c6a47f2d2074020a255ad7a51a","tid":2344370,"uid":86592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T16:23:48.000Z","msg":"當年有個查明夏好扭到仆街"},{"pid":"035d845134de17e1b307ecf931effc2c868653c3","tid":2344370,"uid":653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"拉科魯尼亞帶來更永恆傷感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46199c4c379b89375712ff4b93de2e235920bbb","tid":2344370,"uid":71068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"冇錢？"},{"pid":"91321a29ba8c7